Why Ambush Works

Ambush doesn’t chase—it waits at the convergence point.

It doesn’t solve the problem of catching you…
It solves the problem of where you will be.

That’s the inversion.

* Rabbit strategy = stay unmodeled
* Ambush strategy = model the environment, not the rabbit

